<h4 id="3-process-technology-trend">3. Process Technology Trend</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Gate density doubles at each node</li>
  <li>with more integrated functions and features</li>
  <li>with higher performance</li>
  <li>with lower active and static power</li>
</ul>

